### Welcome to UbiShare homepage at GitHub.
UbiShare is part of [UbiCollab.org](http://www.ubicollab.org).

In these pages you will find the following:
* [User guide for UbiShare](https://github.com/UbiCollab/UbiShare/wiki).
* [Download files](https://github.com/UbiCollab/UbiShare/downloads): Apps and jar library files.
* [Current bugs and issues list](https://github.com/UbiCollab/UbiShare/issues).
* [UbiShare source code](https://github.com/UbiCollab/UbiShare).
* [UbiShare roadmap](https://github.com/UbiCollab/UbiShare/issues/milestones).

### Support or Contact
If you have problems using UbiShare please file an issue with details about your problem.
If you want to know more about UbiShare and UbiCollab, please visit [our web site](http://www.ubicollab.org).
